headline: American Airlines: improved profitability in Q4
summary: American Airlines reports adjusted EPS of $0.86 for the fourth quarter of 2024, compared with $0.29 a year earlier, with adjusted operating margin up 3.3 points to 8.4% on operating revenues up 4.6%...
